me.com/artists/dream">D:Ream</a> 、Goldie Live、Chris Stussy、Mall Grab、Enzo Siragusa Gok Wan、Desiree、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/logic1000">Logic1000、</a> Kurupt FM 等的表演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>已被​​确认成为今年夏天标志性金字塔舞台的主角，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a>将在周日的传奇时段表演。</p><p>酷玩乐队 (Coldplay) 和杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 的演出也将于本周在<a href="https://www.bbc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC.com</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-coldplay-and-dua-lipas-headline-sets-to-be-first-ever-streamed-globally-on-bbc-com-3768213">进行直播</a>，这也是该网站有史以来首次在全球范围内播出。</p><p>今年即将登台的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip</a> 。</p><p>格拉斯顿伯里最近的其他消息显示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/emily-eavis-confirms-glastonbury-is-likely-to-take-a-year-off-in-2026-3764018">该音乐节很可能会在 2026 年暂停一年</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emily-eavis">艾米莉·伊维斯 (Emily Eavis)</a>最近在 BBC 的<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/p0j2p63d" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Sidetracked</em></a>播客上证实，她正在考虑在两年后的沃西农场狂欢节 (Worthy Farm bash) 休耕一年。该节日上一次正式休会是在 2018 年。</p><p> “休耕年很重要，因为它让土地得到休息，也让奶牛有机会在外面呆更长时间并开垦土地，”她说。</p><p>与此同时，对 2024 年的预测（从本周开始）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-weather-forecast-3763664">看起来相当有希望</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-of-groove-armadas-glastonbury-2024-sets-cancelled-due-to-crowd-concerns-3768236">因观众担忧而取消 Groove Armada 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节之一的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
